Tarling\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have qualified for the World Cup here, just after Cadel's, so I will do that and see how it goes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"Cadel\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond Adelaide, Tarling - like Ganna and Viviani - is unlikely to race on the track again until the summer, with his Ineos duties taking precedence.\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2902, \"end\": 2907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adelaide\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling - like Ganna\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"Viviani\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"precedence\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You only have to do one World Cup, so it'll be just training, I think,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one World Cup\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2968}, {\"ngram\": \"just training\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, if the track team needs me I will do it, but it's mainly just training for the track and fitting it in around the road racing.\\\"\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track team\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3045}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"the road racing\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling enjoyed a 